CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 12, 1941, pg. 8, reads: "Pretty Jackson-Cralle Nuptials Bring Socialites Together In Festive Affair - The Jackson-Cralle nuptials last Saturday evening proved one of smoke town's smartest affairs... the bridesmaids Elsie Brown, Emilie Hamilton, Wilhelmina (Billy) Jackson, Lucia Dorcas, and Harriet Cralle... - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women in wedding party, from left: Elsie Brown, Emilie Hamilton, Wilhelmina "Billy" Jackson, Lucia Dorcas, and Harriet Cralle, standing in Loendi Club for Jackson - Cralle wedding
